<view class="page-shell settings-page">
  <view class="settings-section">
    <view class="settings-section__title">学习目标</view>
    <view class="settings-section__hint">为每日 / 每周的专注时长设定目标。0 = 不设。</view>
    <view class="settings-section__body">
      <view wx:for="{{goalRows}}" wx:key="key" class="settings-row">
        <view class="settings-row__text">
          <text class="settings-row__label">{{item.label}}</text>
          <text class="settings-row__desc">{{item.description}}</text>
        </view>
        <view class="settings-row__stepper">
          <view
            class="settings-row__step {{!item.canDecrement ? 'is-disabled' : ''}}"
            data-key="{{item.key}}"
            data-dir="down"
            bindtap="onStepperTap"
          >−</view>
          <view class="settings-row__value-wrap">
            <text class="settings-row__value">{{item.displayValue}}</text>
            <text wx:if="{{item.unit}}" class="settings-row__unit">{{item.unit}}</text>
          </view>
          <view
            class="settings-row__step {{!item.canIncrement ? 'is-disabled' : ''}}"
            data-key="{{item.key}}"
            data-dir="up"
            bindtap="onStepperTap"
          >+</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="settings-section">
    <view class="settings-section__title">学习音景</view>
    <view class="settings-section__hint">专注开始时自动循环播放，结束自动停止。</view>
    <view class="settings-section__body settings-section__body--audio">
      <view
        wx:for="{{audioScenes}}"
        wx:key="key"
        class="audio-scene {{item.active ? 'is-active' : ''}}"
        data-key="{{item.key}}"
        bindtap="onTapAudioScene"
      >
        <text class="audio-scene__emoji">{{item.emoji}}</text>
        <view class="audio-scene__text">
          <text class="audio-scene__label">{{item.label}}</text>
          <text class="audio-scene__desc">{{item.description}}</text>
        </view>
        <view wx:if="{{item.active}}" class="audio-scene__check">✓</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="settings-section">
    <view class="settings-section__title">番茄钟参数</view>
    <view class="settings-section__hint">业界默认是 25-5-15-4，但每个人节奏不同，按自己的来。</view>
    <view class="settings-section__body">
      <view wx:for="{{pomodoroRows}}" wx:key="key" class="settings-row">
        <view class="settings-row__text">
          <text class="settings-row__label">{{item.label}}</text>
          <text class="settings-row__desc">{{item.description}}</text>
        </view>
        <view class="settings-row__stepper">
          <view
            class="settings-row__step {{!item.canDecrement ? 'is-disabled' : ''}}"
            data-key="{{item.key}}"
            data-dir="down"
            bindtap="onStepperTap"
          >−</view>
          <view class="settings-row__value-wrap">
            <text class="settings-row__value">{{item.displayValue}}</text>
            <text wx:if="{{item.unit}}" class="settings-row__unit">{{item.unit}}</text>
          </view>
          <view
            class="settings-row__step {{!item.canIncrement ? 'is-disabled' : ''}}"
            data-key="{{item.key}}"
            data-dir="up"
            bindtap="onStepperTap"
          >+</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="settings-reset" bindtap="onResetTap">恢复默认设置</view>

  <view class="settings-foot">设置仅保存在当前设备。已记录的学习数据存于云端，不受设置影响。</view>
</view>
